                    MOVE 'Sir' TO CUSTTITI
                    CONTINUE
                 WHEN 'SIR       '
                    MOVE 'Sir' TO CUSTTITI
                    CONTINUE
                 WHEN 'Sir       '
                    MOVE 'Sir' TO CUSTTITI
                    CONTINUE
